{"tid":2140482,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"颱風「黑格比」眼壁不斷爆對流 或增強迹象","createTime":"2020-08-05T04:48:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T09:47:58.000Z","uid":250377,"like":347,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":84,"replies":[{"pid":"9b5237bd629d61d59fc4463f30ae735995f480d6","tid":2140482,"uid":250377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T04:48:05.000Z","msg":"昨日（4日）清晨登陸中國浙江溫州的颱風「黑格比」，雖然未加強至超強颱風的最高級別，但已成為自2007年以來正面吹襲溫州最強的風暴。而在黑格比形成之初，原來區內多個氣象部門並不看好其發展；⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n一般而言，海溫至少26&deg;C，才有足夠能量形成熱帶氣旋和維持其強度。美國氣象部門原先預計，黑格比雖受惠逾30&deg;C海溫而增強，⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯強度由熱帶風暴跳升2級至颱風，中心風力亦由時速85公里翻半番至130公里。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200805/ZKWPLKSB2YLF3ENSJZ5LIBRRAA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200805%2FZKWPLKSB2YLF3ENSJZ5LIBRRAA%2F&d=Iz1eZ%2FSDqTYQUikxH7ZeaitC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=3d35d3bb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200805%2FZKWPLKSB2YLF3ENSJZ5LIBRRAA%2F&h=52573294\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200805/ZKWPLKSB2YLF3ENSJZ5LIBRRAA/</a>"},{"pid":"43bd314946950e393096cec7a758b25cdc28c314","tid":2140482,"uid":250377,"like":138,"dislike":0,"score":138,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T04:50:06.000Z","msg":"希望中國無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"002298b504626a99e35e74ce3a627f085ea90c47","tid":2140482,"uid":13663,"like":260,"dislike":0,"score":260,"citedBy":15,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T04:51:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mtvphEX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmtvphEX.png&h=8ceac9fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n打完中國 打北韓<br />\n你老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6529f63cab8b4c7b2b8d92622cc541c05c40300","tid":2140482,"uid":13303,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"quote":{"pid":"002298b504626a99e35e7